<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode.RemoveChildNode" Title="RemoveChildNode method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode">IRenderPassNode</PageRef> ->
    RemoveChildNode
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>RemoveChildNode</TypeRef> method removes the specified <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode">IProgramNode</PageRef>
      from the list of child nodes if it is present.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Warning">
      <Paragraph>
        It is possible to add the same <TypeRef>IProgramNode</TypeRef> as a child more than once to the same <TypeRef>IRenderPassNode</TypeRef>.
        If this is done, for performance reasons, the <TypeRef>RemoveChildNode</TypeRef> method removes the first
        instance of the child node only. As an alternative, the <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode.RemoveChildNodes">RemoveChildNodes</PageRef>
        method will remove all instances of the child node in this case.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void RemoveChildNode(IProgramNode* childNode);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="IProgramNode*!cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode" Name="childNode">
          The <TypeRef>IProgramNode</TypeRef> node to remove from the list of child nodes
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="See also">
    <PageRefList>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IRenderPassNode">IRenderPassNode</PageRefListEntry>
      <PageRefListEntry PageName="cobalt.graphics.IProgramNode">IProgramNode</PageRefListEntry>
    </PageRefList>
  </Section>
</XMLDocContent>
